h2#section-create-project Architecture Overview

p.
  The <strong>VA Application Architecture</strong> involves 3 components:

ol
  li The Application - HTML/JS web application (front-end code)
  li The Middle Tier - Note: If using MDWS (pronounced Meadows), a SOAP client will be needed to interface between the Application and MDWS.
  li The Database
    ul
      li VistA - A database of one hospital facility
      li CDW - A collection of all VistA instances across multiple hospital facilities
      li MongoDB - Application database used for individual application needs
     
